cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.DC

Reasoning: 
1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper focuses on service function chain migration in dynamic traffic, which is a networking problem. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a deep Q-network based algorithm and a multi-agent cooperative framework, both of which are AI techniques. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses deep Q-network, which is a machine learning technique. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with optimizing network operation cost under constraints of users' quality of service, which can be seen as a control problem. 
5. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The multi-agent cooperative framework proposed in the paper can be seen as a distributed computing problem.
